272
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:44,166
Understood.

273
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:47,416
The pilot's mental condition
has also stabilized.

274
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:50,958
He's here!

275
00:20:51,041 --> 00:20:52,750
Open the Number
seven Night Helle.

276
00:20:52,833 --> 00:20:54,125
Do it now!

277
00:20:54,208 --> 00:20:56,208
Fafner Mark Sieben you
